Heren Keep V1.2
Description
Heren Keep V1.2 is a browser extension designed to enhance productivity by automatically saving copied texts and allowing users to manually add notes. It includes features like search functionality, text truncation, and expand/collapse for long notes.

Features
Automatic Text Saving: Automatically saves copied texts along with the website name.

Manual Notes: Add custom notes using the "Keep" button.

Search Functionality: Search through saved texts and notes.

Expand/Collapse Notes: Long notes are truncated to 100 characters, with an option to view the full text.

Copy and Delete Options: Easily copy or delete saved texts and notes.

