Installation Instructions
For Chrome:
Open Chrome and navigate to chrome://extensions/.

Enable Developer Mode using the toggle in the top-right corner.

Click Load unpacked and select your heren V1.2 folder.

For Firefox:
Open Firefox and navigate to about:debugging.

Click This Firefox in the sidebar.

Click Load Temporary Add-on and select your manifest.json file from the heren V1.2 folder.

Usage Instructions
Automatic Text Saving:
Copy any text while browsing; it will be saved automatically along with the website name.

Saved texts appear in the popup with options to copy or delete them.

Manual Notes:
Click the "Keep" button in the popup.

Write your note in the modal that appears and click "Save."

Saved notes will appear below copied texts.

Search Functionality:
Use the search bar at the top of the popup to find specific texts or notes.

Matching results will be highlighted.

Expand/Collapse Notes:
Long notes are truncated to 100 characters with a "Click to expand" option.

Click on a truncated note to view its full content; click again to collapse it.

